<plot>After an explosion in Stanford, CT. kills 600 bystanders, sentiment for superheroes reach an all-time low. The government calls for a Superhero Registration Act, where all superheroes are required to register with the federal government as a "human weapon of mass destruction", reveal his/her true identity to the authorities, and undergo proper training. However, not everyone is satisfied with this law. Therefore, players can either side with Iron Man or Mr. Fantastic on the Pro-Registration, or Captain America and Luke Cage on the Anti-Registration side.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?359635</url></doc>
